flowchart TD
    NODE[Current node execution] --> CONTRACTS[Load field contracts<br/>Input schema, operation contract, ownership, validation, repair hints]
    CONTRACTS --> LINEAGE[Build lineage context<br/>User intent, trigger output, upstream outputs, last successful business output, upstream errors]
    LINEAGE --> FIND_FIELDS[Find missing or invalid runtime_ai fields<br/>All fields collected together]
    FIND_FIELDS --> REPAIR[Deterministic repair first<br/>Extract emails, object-to-row values, derive body/title/condition]
    REPAIR --> AI_NEEDED{Still missing safe AI-owned fields?}
    AI_NEEDED -->|Yes| AI_JSON[Strict structured AI resolver<br/>One JSON object for all requested fields]
    AI_NEEDED -->|No| VALIDATE
    AI_JSON --> VALIDATE[Universal validation<br/>Required, protected, format, placeholder, empty, unsafe values]
    VALIDATE --> RETRY{Invalid AI output?}
    RETRY -->|Yes| AI_RETRY[Retry with exact invalid fields]
    AI_RETRY --> VALIDATE
    RETRY -->|No| AUDIT[Runtime input audit<br/>Field, source, repair, validation, preview]
    AUDIT --> FINAL[Final resolved input object]
